node.text:
Today, I felt like sharing some of my favorite animal photos that I’ve collected over the years.📸
I know animal photography isn’t really my area of expertise, and there are people out there who are a thousand times better at it than I am, but I still wanted to share these pictures here so they’re not just sitting on my hard drive gathering dust😅

#photography #naturephotography #wildlife #animalphotography #nature
Ultra detail shots 🔥 great work on these wildlife
@someone_shoots.png thanks so much😍 was a great moment😍
Great set 😍 but the cow in front of the mountains is just perfect 😮‍💨
What camera and lens did you use if you don’t mind me asking? Great photos either way 🫶🏼🫶🏼
Sir can you give me these pics in original quality, 🙏
You did well! 👏🏼📸They are great! Very good shots!🔥
